(796, 2, 'Macros and Preprocessors in C', 'http://www.geeksforgeeks.org/interesting-facts-preprocessors-c/', 'geeksforgeeks.org', 'In a C program, all lines that start with # are processed by preprocessor which is a special program invoked by the compiler. In a very basic term, preprocessor takes a C program and produces another C program without any #. Following are some interesting facts about preprocessors in C. 1) When we use includeâ€¦ Read More &raquo;', ' C '),
