(816, 2, 'Understanding "register" keyword in C', 'http://www.geeksforgeeks.org/understanding-register-keyword/', 'geeksforgeeks.org', 'Registers are faster than memory to access, so the variables which are most frequently used in a C program can be put in registers using register keyword. The keyword register hints to compiler that a given variable can be put in a register. It&#8217;s compiler&#8217;s choice to put it in a register or not. Generally,â€¦ Read More &raquo;', ' C '),
